i.</p><span class=tag>Fun</span><span class=tag>SysAdmin</span></a><a class=card href=https://github.com/robbiepryan/Roku-MCP><h3>Roku MCP</h3><p>Model Context Protocol server for controlling Roku devices — AI meets your living room.</p><span class=tag>MCP</span><span class=tag>Automation</span></a><a class=card href=https://github.com/robbiepryan/techflow-1kb><h3>This Site</h3><p>The page you're looking at — a full interactive particle network in under 1.4KB, loading content dynamically from JSON.</p><span class=tag>HTML</span><span class=tag>Canvas</span><span class=tag>1.4KB</span></a></div><p class=foot>Built with particles & stubbornness</p>"
